---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---
<footer class="border-t border-line mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1240px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-10 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 text-sm">
    <div>
      <img src="/images/logo-cygne.png" alt="Laverie du Cygne" class="h-14 w-auto mb-4" />
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Laverie automatique au Centre Commercial le Cygne, ouverte 7 jours sur 7.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Adresse</p>
      <p class="text-muted-strong">1 rue Léo Lagrange<br/>10600 La Chapelle-Saint-Luc</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Horaires</p>
      <p class="text-muted-strong">Tous les jours<br/>7h00, 22h00</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Contact</p>
      <a href="tel:0983475722" class="block text-muted-strong hover:text-accent transition-colors">09 83 47 57 22</a>
      <a href="mailto:laverieducygne@gmail.com" class="block text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors text-xs mt-1">laverieducygne@gmail.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-line">
    <div class="max-w-[1240px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-muted">
      <p>&copy; {year} Laverie du Cygne · La Chapelle-Saint-Luc · <a href="/mentions-legales" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Mentions légales</a></p>
      <p>Site réalisé par <a href="https://veridian.site" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Veridian</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
